gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 138, Jazz 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Jazz, 138-122. Anthony Davis led the way 37 points and 15 rebounds for the Lakers, with Rui Hachimura adding a career-high 36 points and career-high six 3PM in the victory. Collin Sexton tallied 18 points and three assists for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Lakers have won three in a row and improve to 30-26, while the Jazz fall 26-29.
